summary: This module defines a set of Django model classes and a base manager used in the migration test suite. It includes a foundational manager for foodâ€‘related data, a model with a Unicode text field and a custom string representation, a placeholder model for an app that lacks migration files, and a dummy class representing objects that cannot be serialized during a migration.
business_intent: Supply concrete model definitions that allow the Django migration framework to be exercised and validated against edge cases such as custom managers, Unicode handling, missing migrations, and unserializable objects.
